== Application Process:
   
   If you are interested in a position, please feel free to contact Wenqi at: wenqi.fan(at)polyu(dot)edu(dot)hk. 
   
   Below are some suggestions when contacting via email:
   
   ~~~

   Please…
    . Use a subject line as follows: \{\$position\} Open Position \{\$YourName\}，
       where {$position} should be ‘‘Postdoc’’, ‘‘PhD’’, ‘‘MPhil’’, ‘‘MSs’’, ‘‘BS’’, ‘‘Visiting’’, or ‘‘RA’’.\n
          e.g., If I were applying for a Research Assistant position I would use the subject ‘‘RA Open Position Hengyun Li’’
    . Provide a few sentences to introduce yourself and express your interest in the position
    . Attach your CV\/Resume
        Including the following (if applicable): GPA\/ranking, TOEFL\/IELTS\/GRE scores, and publications\/research experience, awards, etc.
   ~~~


Thank you and I look forward to hearing from you!


